cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on machine learning and optimization techniques for black-box adversarial attacks on neural network image classifiers. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with image classification, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the security aspect of the neural network, which can be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The proposed algorithm involves optimization techniques, which can be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
